title: Independent Candidate Khurram Shahzad Virk wins NA-115 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): An Independent Candidate Khurram Shahzad Virk has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-115, Sheikhupura III by securing 130,255 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz Candidate Javed Latif, who bagged 94,144, votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 50.34, percent.
